Installation instructions:

This torrent will create a Windows directory usb-multiboot-2015-eclectic-64 with all setup files and documentation. The best guide is to read from the link above, a copy of which is included in the download. There is no need to unzip or unrar anything. There are no keys or passwords. Start USB installation by clicking on Click-START.cmd 

This Gooplusplus 10GB download consists of tools and Linux distributions to create (with Windows or Linux) a bootable USB flash drive (minimum 16GB).

 * Click-START-WinXP menu is for Windows XP only.
